Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.35,0:01:34.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,登富士山的日子終於到了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.44,0:01:41.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從新宿出發 大約兩個半小時
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.69,0:01:44.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,上午十點過後 我們到達了富士五合目
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:49.29,title,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an8\pos(560,430)}初次見面 富士山
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.91,0:01:51.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好涼快啊
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.24,0:01:55.66,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為五合目已經是標高2300米左右了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.96,0:01:58.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,應該比下面低10度以上哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.79,0:02:03.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山的高度好像是3776米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.13,0:02:07.13,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一半的話 是1888米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:10.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,五合目不是一半的高度對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.51,0:02:14.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 幾合目和高度距離好像沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.23,0:02:19.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有一種說法是按照登山的難度為標準決定的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.11,0:02:22.78,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比如說 從五合目到六合目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從六合目到七合目
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.78,0:02:28.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有從七合目到八合目 雖然距離很短
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.20,0:02:32.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,路卻越來越艱險 一樣的疲憊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.37,0:02:36.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,越往上越艱險啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.96,0:02:39.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,加…加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.55,0:02:46.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是郵局啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.01,0:02:48.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有兌換所
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.14,0:02:50.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自行車
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.39,0:02:54.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到這裏為止自行車也可以通行呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.52,0:02:56.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬兒
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.77,0:03:01.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到七合目為止 可以騎馬哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.77,0:03:02.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.94,0:03:06.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過用自己的雙腿登上去 一定會更加感動的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.07,0:03:07.61,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.86,0:03:11.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就一邊讓身體適應 一邊吃飯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.91,0:03:15.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山因為標高很高 容易得高山病呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:17.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,高山病？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.37,0:03:20.71,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在標高很高的地方勉強登山的話
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.92,0:03:23.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會頭疼 變得很不舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.96,0:03:28.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大部分的情況 到山腳下一下就會好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.84,0:03:30.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家可不要勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.55,0:03:31.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.18,0:03:35.18,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃什麼好呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.76,0:03:37.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃什麼呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.93,0:03:42.15,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看啊 爆炸咖喱 很有趣啊 我吃這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.44,0:03:44.69,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃野菜蕎面吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.94,0:03:46.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雲海拉麵？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.03,0:03:49.53,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,咦 是什麼樣的拉麵呢
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.65,0:03:51.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以說成是雲海
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.91,0:03:52.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,餛飩嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.95,0:03:53.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雞蛋湯？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.91,0:03:54.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是山藥
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.45,0:03:56.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,鮮奶油
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.83,0:04:00.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛 我要吃雲海拉麵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.00,0:04:02.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那我也要
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.13,0:04:05.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好期待雲海拉麵是什麼呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.79,0:04:06.67,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:09.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我開動了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.67,0:04:11.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是爆炸咖喱
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:16.76,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,米飯是富士山 福神漬是熔岩啊 原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.56,0:04:19.06,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雲海拉麵是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.60,0:04:24.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是普通的拉麵啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.94,0:04:28.73,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雖然是普通的拉麵 但是很好吃呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.82,0:04:30.82,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 吃得好飽
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.28,0:04:35.45,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,土特產有各種各樣的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.57,0:04:38.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這個好可愛
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.83,0:04:40.08,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.58,0:04:42.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真好 買一個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.87,0:04:44.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回來再買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.58,0:04:47.46,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊 會成為負擔的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.71,0:04:48.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.96,0:04:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.47,0:04:52.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.38,0:04:54.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(522,617)\frz3.4}可以成為紀念
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(95,56)}附加鈴鐺
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(148,111)}附加鈴鐺 旗幟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\pos(148,168)}附加鈴鐺 帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.51,0:04:55.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是金剛杖
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.05,0:04:58.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以在登頂途中的山間小屋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.81,0:05:01.27,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把烙印印在這只杖上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.48,0:05:06.48,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我想把烙印都集齊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.52,0:05:09.02,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也買吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把烙印都集齊的話 會成為很好的紀念哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.41,0:05:15.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz355.236\pos(642,294)}希望可以平安登頂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz352.801\pos(841,434)}葵    楓
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.50,0:05:21.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\frz352.97\pos(818,591)}日向   心夏
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.25,0:05:24.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 現在開始登山
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.75,0:05:26.83,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 媽媽
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.25,0:05:29.21,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會再打給你的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.88,0:05:34.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就向富士山頂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.47,0:05:36.09,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,出發！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.22,0:05:40.35,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘿 麥克 等等我 再慢一點
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.52,0:05:44.77,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在還很輕鬆呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.98,0:05:49.32,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,要是最後也是這樣 就輕鬆了…不可能這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.07,0:05:57.41,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,富士山分為須走路線 御殿場路線等幾個登山路線
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.70,0:06:01.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們登的是最普通的吉田路線
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.79,0:06:07.25,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從五合目開始 經過六合目 七合目 八合目到達本八合目
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.50,0:06:12.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在那裏留宿山間小屋 好好休養再上山頂出發
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.42,0:06:14.47,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為山間小屋有很多
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.63,0:06:17.68,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們打算一邊進行適當的休息一邊登山
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.31,0:06:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏就是六合目了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.85,0:06:29.56,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微休息一會吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.40,0:06:33.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才只走了30分鐘哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.44,0:06:36.03,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用急 山是不會逃走的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.32,0:06:38.36,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,前路很長呢 對吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.28,0:06:41.74,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我吃點心好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.91,0:06:43.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就要吃了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.24,0:06:46.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯 在肚子餓之前吃是很重要的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.79,0:06:48.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你這不是從楓那現學現賣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.04,0:06:51.63,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵筋
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.09,0:06:52.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,麵筋？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.13,0:06:54.51,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,跟老爺爺似的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.34,0:06:59.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,厲害 膨脹了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看 你看
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.85,0:07:03.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是因為氣壓差吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.93,0:07:06.14,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.02,0:07:09.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來正要向著七合目出發
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.52,0:07:10.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.77,0:07:13.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難受的話 哪怕在路上也要返回哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.27,0:07:15.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,絕對不可以勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.86,0:07:17.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你太擔心了啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.03,0:07:21.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會再給你打電話的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:23.58,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.33,0:07:25.79,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,差不多該走了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.12,0:07:26.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.96,0:07:33.84,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直都在走一樣的路呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.50,0:07:36.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都是岩石呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.42,0:07:38.38,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,推土機
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.38,0:07:42.43,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用那個往山間小屋運送食物和水呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.85,0:07:44.81,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能不能讓我們坐上去呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.77,0:07:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,七合目到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.61,0:07:57.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是第二個了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.03,0:07:58.57,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.20,0:08:06.24,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,第三個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.24,0:08:07.37,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很順利呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.87,0:08:12.29,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,山間小屋真的有很多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.33,0:08:14.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺十步就有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.22,0:08:22.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.30,0:08:23.05,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,楓？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.39,0:08:24.34,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.93,0:08:26.64,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,滑雪杖的頂端掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.68,0:08:28.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,糟了 大家一起找吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.10,0:08:32.23,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這根滑雪杖還挺貴的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.73,0:08:33.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.23,0:08:36.40,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這麼容易就找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.40,0:08:36.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.07,0:08:37.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裏也有
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.64,0:09:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.72,0:09:08.26,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.93,0:09:10.72,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,休息一下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.68,0:09:12.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.94,0:09:22.65,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.16,0:09:26.16,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,冷不冷？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:27.62,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.95,0:09:28.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.12,0:09:31.12,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難受的話不要顧慮儘管說哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.33,0:09:32.00,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.21,0:09:41.80,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能行
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.51,0:09:44.42,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵 出發了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.43,0:09:49.22,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,葵？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.51,0:09:51.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒事的 我只是晃了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.94,0:09:58.52,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個真的是登山道？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.23,0:10:00.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就好像是山崖一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.95,0:10:08.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這根杖變得礙事了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.92,0:10:18.75,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相當辛苦呢
